accessibility.text: This is the animation pass for Dance #2 based off the reference footage.
The following notes are already being worked on:
More attention and expression needed in the hand and wrist movement.
Hands should be swiping rhythmically upwards instead of slapping downwards.
Add slight foot shift and slide
Reduce speed - quantize to a 95-100bpm range and on half-time beat
